---
import { Container, TextSection, FeatureCard } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';

const seo = {
	title: 'Solutions | NMES for Astronauts',
	description: 'Current countermeasures and the NMES solution',
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
	<Container>
		<TextSection narrow>
		<h1 style="text-align: center;">
      Countermeasures: Fighting the Fade
    </h1>
		<p>
			To combat muscle loss, space agencies currently rely on one main tool: <strong>exercise</strong>. But is it enough? And what if there's a better way?
		</p>
    </TextSection>

    <section class="comparison-section">
      <div class="card traditional">
        <h2>The Old Way: Exercise</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Heavy Lifting:</strong> Astronauts must strap themselves into massive resistance machines.</li>
          <li><strong>Time Consuming:</strong> Requires 2+ hours of intense sweating every single day.</li>
          <li><strong>Incomplete:</strong> Even with this effort, some muscle loss still occurs.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="limitations">
          <h3>The Drawback</h3>
          <p>It eats up valuable mission time and requires equipment too heavy for a Mars mission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card nmes">
        <h2>The Future: NMES</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Passive Power:</strong> Electrical impulses trigger muscle contractions without you moving a muscle.</li>
          <li><strong>Compact:</strong> The device is the size of a smartphone, not a gym.</li>
          <li><strong>Smart:</strong> Can target specific muscle fibers that exercise misses.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="benefits">
          <h3>The Advantage</h3>
          <p>Wear it while you work. Maintain muscle mass without sacrificing mission time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
	</Container>
</Layout>

<style>
  .icon-header {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
    color: var(--theme-primary);
  }
	.comparison-grid {
		display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .comparison-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--theme-shape-radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--theme-surface-2);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .traditional {
    background-color: var(--theme-surface-1);
  }

  .nmes {
    background-color: var(--theme-surface-2);
    border-color: var(--theme-primary);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .limitations, .benefits {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .limitations h3, .benefits h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style>
